  "prompt": "Who is the best doctor for cardiology in India?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" cardiologist in India can be subjective, as it depends on individual needs, location, and specific heart conditions. However, several renowned cardiologists have made significant contributions to the field and are highly respected. A few notable names include:\n\n1. **Dr. Devi Shetty** - Founder of Narayana Health, he is known for his work in cardiac surgery and affordable healthcare.\n2. **Dr. Naresh Trehan** - A well-known cardiac surgeon and the chairman of Medanta - The Medicity, he has extensive experience in cardiovascular surgery.\n3. **Dr. Ashok Seth** - An interventional cardiologist known for his expertise in complex angioplasties and other heart procedures.\n4. **Dr. J. C. Mohanty** - A prominent cardiologist with expertise in interventional cardiology.\n5. **Dr. K. K. Talwar** - Former Director of PGIMER, Chandigarh, and an influential figure in medical education and cardiology.\n\nIt is advisable to seek recommendations based on specific needs, read patient reviews, and consult multiple sources to find the right cardiologist for you.",
